    <title>关卡三 部署战略</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/03/28/%E5%85%B3%E5%8D%A1%E4%B8%89%20%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%88%98%E7%95%A5/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/03/28/%E5%85%B3%E5%8D%A1%E4%B8%89%20%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%88%98%E7%95%A5/</id>
    <published>2020-03-28T01:28:36.309Z</published>
    <updated>2020-04-02T13:13:10.789Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这一关卡是困我数周的大关，本人经验总结如下：</p><blockquote><p>不慌，不是你一个人</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>别急，不是你一个人</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>不行，删除重新再来</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>记住，不是你一个人遇到这样的问题</p></blockquote><more><p>以下是我探索的过程，希望对你们有所帮助</p><p>1.注册github:访问<a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/</a></p><p><img src="../image/%E4%B8%89/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720200328104645.png" alt=""></p><p>以上注册不给予详细步骤</p><p>2.新建仓库</p><p>登录自己的github，点击下图</p><p><img src="../image/%E4%B8%89/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720200328105740.png" alt=""></p><p>输入仓库名称,点击create  repository</p><p><img src="../image/%E4%B8%89/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720200328105909.png" alt=""></p><p><img src="../image/%E4%B8%89/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720200328105914.png" alt=""></p><p>出现下面的字样，表示你创建的仓库具有展示的功能</p><p><img src="../image/%E4%B8%89/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720200328105920.png" alt="QQ图片20200328105920"></p><p>3.添加ssh公钥</p><p>输入一下指令</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd ~</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"你的邮箱"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>邮箱为注册GitHub的邮箱，指令输入后出现下图结果</p><p><img src="../picture/20200313214311.png" alt=""></p><p><img src="../image/%E4%B8%89/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720200328111507.png" alt=""></p><p>根据图上的地址就可以找到我们需要的public key,打开复制。</p><p>接着将ssh公钥添加到GitHub账户中去，同下系列照做</p><p><img src="../image/%E4%B8%89/2.png" alt=""></p><p><img src="../image/%E4%B8%89/1.png" alt=""></p><p><img src="../image/%E4%B8%89/4.png" alt=""></p><p><img src="../image/%E4%B8%89/5.png" alt=""></p><p>出现下图内容即完成</p><p><img src="../image/%E4%B8%89/3.png" alt=""></p><p>4.绑定hexo 和GitHub</p><p>（难点来了）</p><ul><li>修改本地站点配置文件：打开blog&gt;_config</li><li><img src="../image/%E4%B8%89/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720200328113253.png" alt=""></li></ul><p>​           其中username是自己GitHub的用户名。注意：每个“：”后面都有一个空格。</p><ul><li><p>输入以下指令</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git -save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>出现版本号，为成功。</p><p>5.一念天堂，一念地狱</p><p>输入</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>浏览<a href="https://username.github.io。" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://username.github.io。</a></p><p>如果出现博客页面，恭喜你成功了。如果没有，抱歉，重来吧！不过不要气馁，抱着“无心插柳柳成荫”的态度无限循环上面的步骤，不过不是盲目执行，科学上网，科学求助。</p><p>此处附上两位大佬的博客：</p><p><a href="http://www.yangkai123.top/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://www.yangkai123.top/</a></p><p><a href="https://xiaotaiyangzhijia.top/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://xiaotaiyangzhijia.top/</a></p></li></ul>]]></content>
    
